<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1043.64438.figure6>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 6. Spinoncaea ivlevi (Shmeleva, 1966), female, robust form (Korea Strait) A antenna [a: first endopod segment of right antenna, additional broad spinules arrowed] B maxilla, long setule arrowed C labrum, anterior, additional setules arrowed D P 5 - bearing somite, ventral, midventral spinous processes and weakly pronounced ventrolateral lobes arrowed. Scale bars in μm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/555763" .

